{"id":15109,"date":"2022-09-06T00:25:27","date_gmt":"2022-09-05T17:25:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=15109"},"modified":"2022-09-06T00:25:27","modified_gmt":"2022-09-05T17:25:27","slug":"dich-vu-thiet-ke-cv-bang-tieng-nhat","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-cv-bang-tieng-nhat.html\/","title":{"rendered":"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf CV b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-cv-bang-tieng-nhat.html\/#CV_tieng_Nhat_la_gi\" title=\"CV ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\">CV ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-cv-bang-tieng-nhat.html\/#Nguyen_tac_viet_CV_xin_viec\" title=\"Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc vi\u1ebft CV xin vi\u1ec7c\">Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc vi\u1ebft CV xin vi\u1ec7c<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-cv-bang-tieng-nhat.html\/#Cach_viet_so_yeu_ly_lich_tieng_Nhat\" title=\"C\u00e1ch vi\u1ebft s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt\">C\u00e1ch vi\u1ebft s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-cv-bang-tieng-nhat.html\/#Chon_dich_vu_thiet_ke_CV_bang_tieng_Nhat_tai_Achaumedia\" title=\"Ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf CV b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt t\u1ea1i Achaumedia\">Ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf CV b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt t\u1ea1i Achaumedia<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-cv-bang-tieng-nhat.html\/#Chon_chung_toi_ban_se_duoc\" title=\"Ch\u1ecdn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c:\">Ch\u1ecdn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c:<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf CV b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng? L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 trong ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng Achaumedia t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-1\" class=\"ftwp-heading ftwp-heading-target\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CV_tieng_Nhat_la_gi\"><\/span><strong>CV ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15112\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15112\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15112 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1-1.png\" alt=\"Thi\u1ebft-ke-CV-bang-tieng-Nhat\" width=\"800\" height=\"1121\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1-1.png 800w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1-1-214x300.png 214w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1-1-731x1024.png 731w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/1-1-768x1076.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15112\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf CV b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Khi xin vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n hai t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u: S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt.<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt (Rirekisho): T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t l\u00fd l\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n (h\u1ecdc v\u1ea5n, kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c) v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n (t\u00ean, ng\u00e0y sinh, th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7, v.v.)<\/li>\n<li>CV ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt (Shokumu-keirekisho): T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 (c\u00f4ng ty b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, v.v.)<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>Trong s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, h\u00e3y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chia s\u1ebb n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ty b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u1ee9ng tuy\u1ec3n, sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd thu h\u00fat c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u1ee9ng tuy\u1ec3n v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb trong CV ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"ftoc-heading-2\" class=\"ftwp-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nguyen_tac_viet_CV_xin_viec\"><\/span>Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc vi\u1ebft CV xin vi\u1ec7c<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>CV xin vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt\u00a0<\/strong>n\u00ean tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng, b\u1eaft m\u1eaft, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung.<\/li>\n<li>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c font ch\u1eef ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n.<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9 d\u00e0i CV kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 2 trang A4.<\/li>\n<li>Ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ed7i ch\u00ednh t\u1ea3, ng\u1eef ph\u00e1p.<\/li>\n<li>Ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ef9 ph\u1ea7n th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean l\u1ea1c.<\/li>\n<li>T\u00ean file CV \u0111\u1eb7t theo nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc: V\u1ecb Tr\u00ed \u1ee8ng Tuy\u1ec3n + CV + T\u00ean \u1ee8ng Vi\u00ean. V\u00ed d\u1ee5: NhanVienLeTan-CV-TranVanA<\/li>\n<li>Ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ef9 n\u1ed9i dung CV, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u00f4ng tin g\u1eedi nh\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 t\u00ean CV, nhi\u1ec1u khi b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng CV g\u1eedi cho nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t CV n\u1ed9p cho nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_viet_so_yeu_ly_lich_tieng_Nhat\"><\/span><span id=\"How_to_Write_the_Japanese_Resume_for_Foreigners\">C\u00e1ch vi\u1ebft s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c nhau gi\u1eefa thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf CV v\u00e0 s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/li>\n<li>L\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp \/ l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p ho\u1eb7c B\u1eb1ng c\u1ea5p<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, T\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, Th\u1eddi gian \u0111i l\u00e0m, v.v.<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng gian cho c\u00e1c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15110\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15110\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15110 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/rirekisho_0-2-1024x635-1.jpg\" alt=\"Cach-viet-so-yeu-ly-lich-bang-tieng-Nhat\" width=\"1024\" height=\"635\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/rirekisho_0-2-1024x635-1.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/rirekisho_0-2-1024x635-1-300x186.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/rirekisho_0-2-1024x635-1-768x476.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15110\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch vi\u1ebft s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadt<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chon_dich_vu_thiet_ke_CV_bang_tieng_Nhat_tai_Achaumedia\"><\/span><strong>Ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf CV b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt t\u1ea1i Achaumedia<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media lu\u00f4n \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ty c\u00f3 b\u1ec1 d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/p>\n<p>CV l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng ty c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn v\u00e0o. V\u00ec v\u1eady n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng vi\u1ebft CV c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec h\u00e3y thu\u00ea m\u1ed9t b\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i \u00edch m\u00e0 CV \u0111em l\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chon_chung_toi_ban_se_duoc\"><\/span>Ch\u1ecdn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">CV thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo xu h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">CV \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa n\u1ed9i dung trong CV<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft v\u00e0 bi\u00ean t\u1eadp b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">N\u1ed9i dung th\u00f4ng tin ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd<\/li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf trong th\u1eddi gian quy \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>V\u1edbi quy tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 b\u00ean \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf CV. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng ngay khi h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c. V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong ng\u00e0nh \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd h\u00f5 tr\u1ee3 cho b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 xin vi\u1ec7c.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng m\u1ee5c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Achaumedia, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft mang t\u1edbi cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m.<\/p>\n<p>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft li\u00ean quan:<\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-so-yeu-ly-lich-bang-tieng-trung.html\/\"><em><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Trung<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/4-meo-viet-so-yeu-ly-lich-cho-mot-cong-viec-ky-thuat-cap-dau-vao.html\/\"><em><strong>4 m\u1eb9o vi\u1ebft s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch cho m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cv-so-voi-so-yeu-ly-lich-su-khac-biet-chinh-de-lua-chon-giua-hai.html\/\"><em><strong>CV so v\u1edbi s\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch: S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gi\u1eefa hai<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf CV b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng? L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 trong ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng Achaumed